<section style="padding:72px 24px 40px;"><div style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;"><div class="rich"><p>Crete sits about 25 miles southwest of Lincoln on Highway 33, and we handle <strong>egress window installation in Crete</strong> for homeowners and landlords across Saline County. A lot of Crete's housing stock predates modern building code, and basements along the streets near downtown and the Big Blue River were often finished for bedrooms without a proper emergency exit.</p><p>With Doane University drawing student renters and the local workforce keeping demand high for affordable housing, basement bedrooms are common in Crete rentals, and each one needs a code-compliant egress window to legally count as a sleeping room. We install and replace egress windows and window wells sized to Nebraska building code, with free written estimates so you know the cost before we start. Call <strong>(509) 224-3484</strong> to schedule a look at your basement.</p></div></div></section>
<section style="padding:0 24px 64px;"><div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
