        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">New egress openings cut into Crete basement walls for homeowners finishing a basement bedroom or landlords bringing a rental up to code before it's leased again.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:10px;padding:26px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(14,77,110,0.05);">
